The following addition-curable silicone pre-polymers were mixed by hand:
a vinyl-terminated polydimethylsiloxane 500 cSt (DMS-V25, Gelest, CAS No. 68083-19-2) at about 8.8 wt. % of the silicone premix;
(25-35% methylhydrosiloxane)-dimethylsiloxane copolymer, trimethylsiloxane terminated, 25-35 cSt (HMS-301, Gelest, CAS No. 68037-59-2) at about 0.3 wt. % of the silicone premix;
M3 at about 90.9 wt. % of the silicone premix.
